  "texts": [
    "Contrasting to her prior utterance, she 'jumps' in pitch and repeatedly shifts her gaze.",
    "The wording \"cause I would ask\" is musical and bridges to a new shift in Paula's use of pronouns that evokes the group's presence (Fig. 4).",
    "In this episode, Paula changes not only her prosody but also gaze.",
    "While at the beginning of the speech burst, she looks at the ceiling, at the end of the utterance she directs her gaze at (after 463 ms).",
    "She orients to her left, which allows her to gradually place her absent group members."
